							</div>
							<div class="medium-7 columns">
								<div class="flex-video widescreen vimeo">
								  <iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/310037291" width="400" height="225" frameborder="0" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></iframe>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="dades-container">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="medium-5 columns">
								<h4>2. Registre i configuració del compte</h4>
